        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">What We Do</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          We provide comprehensive support across all aspects of the newcomer journey
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 p-8 border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.746 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.246 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Comprehensive Resources</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            We provide detailed guides on immigration, settlement, employment, and daily life in Canada. 
            Our resources are regularly updated to reflect the latest policies and best practices.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 p-8 border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Community Building</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            We connect newcomers with established Canadians and fellow immigrants to build support networks, 
            share experiences, and create lasting friendships.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 p-8 border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-yellow-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-yellow-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
