            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Success Stories</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            We share real stories from newcomers who have successfully built their lives in Canada, 
            providing inspiration and practical insights for others on similar journeys.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 p-8 border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8.228 9c.549-1.165 2.03-2 3.772-2 2.21 0 4 1.343 4 3 0 1.4-1.278 2.575-3.006 2.907-.542.104-.994.54-.994 1.093m0 3h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Expert Guidance</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Our content is created and reviewed by immigration experts, settlement workers, and successful 
            newcomers to ensure accuracy and relevance.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 p-8 border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-red-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Up-to-Date Information</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            We stay current with immigration policies, job market trends, and settlement services to 
            provide the most relevant and timely information.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 p-8 border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-indigo-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-indigo-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Cultural Support</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            We help newcomers understand Canadian culture, workplace norms, and social expectations 
            while celebrating the diversity they bring to our communities.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Our Story Section -->
    <section class="mb-20">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-blue-50 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8 text-center">Our Story</h2>
          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-center">
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed">
              Northern Landing was founded in 2020 by a group of immigrants and settlement workers who recognized 
              the need for comprehensive, accessible resources for newcomers to Canada. Having experienced the 
              challenges of immigration and settlement firsthand, our founders understood the importance of 
              community support and accurate information.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed">
              What started as a small blog sharing personal experiences has grown into a comprehensive platform 
              serving thousands of newcomers across Canada. We've partnered with settlement agencies, 
              professional associations, and community organizations to provide the most up-to-date and 
              relevant information.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
              Today, Northern Landing continues to evolve, adding new resources, expanding our community, 
              and adapting to the changing needs of newcomers. We're proud to be part of the journey for 
              so many people building their new lives in Canada.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Get Involved Section -->
    <section class="mb-20">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 via-blue-700 to-indigo-800 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 text-white shadow-2xl">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Get Involved</h2>
          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-blue-100 max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
            Whether you're a newcomer looking for support or an established Canadian wanting to help, 
            there are many ways to get involved with Northern Landing.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 hover:bg-white/20 transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white/20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Share Your Story</h3>
            <p class="text-blue-100 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
              Help other newcomers by sharing your immigration and settlement experience.
            </p>
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center bg-white text-blue-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors">
              Contact Us
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 hover:bg-white/20 transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white/20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
